{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1543373781","title":"给鞍山钢铁公司炼钢厂全体职工的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"885977f416","index":0,"year":1952,"month":12,"day":14,"articleId":"1543373781"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"fedabf876e","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"来信向毛泽东汇报了1952年11月22日鞍山钢铁公司炼钢厂在苏联专家帮助下，创造了6小时9分钟炼一炉钢的平炉炼钢全国新纪录的喜讯。"},{"id":"b3cff5d3e1","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指鞍山钢铁公司炼钢厂给毛泽东写信报喜的前一两天，四号平炉生产一炉钢时在炼钢时间和炉底面积利用系数等生产技术指标方面创造的新纪录。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9d1a4ba403","type":"title","text":"给鞍山钢铁公司炼钢厂全体职工的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781"},{"id":"fedabf876e","type":"paragraph","text":"鞍山钢铁公司炼钢厂全体职工同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781"},{"id":"b3cff5d3e1","type":"paragraph","text":"我很高兴地读了你们十二月二日的来信”。祝贺你们在平炉炼钢生产上的最新成就。你们以高度的劳动热情和创造精神，在苏联专家的帮助之下，创造了超过资本主义各国水平的炼钢时间和炉底面积利用系数的新纪录。这不仅是你们的光荣，而且是我国工业化道路上的一件大事。希望你们继续努力，为完成一九五三年度炼好优质钢的新任务而奋斗","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781"},{"id":"74a5e86b7e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781"},{"id":"f0d208bc51","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年十二月十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781"}],"page":{"id":"f6a4d19931","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"1543373781","start":372,"end":372}}}},"__N_SSG":true}